                <h3>Why should you use credit cards during travel?</h3>
                <p>Credit cards offer numerous benefits for travellers, including hassle-free payments, easy currency conversion, and the ability to earn travel rewards and points. Using a travel credit card can simplify your journey and help you save money.</p>
                <h3>How does a travel credit card help with currency conversion?</h3>
                <p>A travel credit card makes currency conversion easy and eliminates the need to carry cash in multiple currencies. It ensures smooth payments abroad without the stress of exchanging currency manually or paying high debit card charges.</p>
                <h3>What rewards can you earn by using a credit card during your trip?</h3>
                <p>You can earn travel rewards and bonus points on various purchases made with your credit card. These points can be redeemed for flights, hotel stays, or other travel-related expenses, helping you save significantly on future trips.</p>
                <h3>What are the airline-specific benefits of using a credit card?</h3>
