                <h3>What is the biggest advantage of using a credit card over cash during travel?</h3>
                <p>The biggest advantage is convenience and safety. A credit card eliminates the need to carry large amounts of cash and ensures secure payments. Additionally, it provides added benefits like rewards, travel perks, and ease of use across multiple countries.</p>
                <h3>Can using a credit card help frequent flyers plan big vacations?</h3>
                <p>Yes, frequent flyers can accumulate miles or points with every trip by using a travel credit card. These rewards can eventually be redeemed for big vacations, making travel more affordable over time.</p>
